<note n="0664009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0664009">Sarvamāramaṇḍalavikiraṇajñānadhvaja, or rāja.</note>
<note n="0664010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0664010">切＝一【明】【和】</note>
